- 'crack' refers to successfully completing or solving;
- 'challenges' refers to 'benchmarks';
- 'managed to crack successfully' refers to the status 'success'.

- 'gardeners' refer to the users;
- 'seeds' are metaphorical representations of benchmarks, and 'sowing seeds' refers to creating benchmarks;
- The condition of creating more than 3 benchmarks is symbolically expressed as sowing more than three seeds.
